ABOUT.THE_GOOGLE_CHROME: The Google Chrome browser extension is a personal assistant for you and your company's employees. Thanks to the extension, regardless of what kind of web CRM you use, you can monitor calls that you need to call back, listen to call records, quickly find interesting information on calls. Pop-up notifications with the caller's name, dialing by clicking on a phone number will save a lot of your time and increase the level of service for your company.
